com.advantage.framework

Class ElapsedTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.advantage.framework.ElapsedTime

  • public class ElapsedTime
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for functions around Elapsed Time. The main purpose of this class is to provide a simple re-usable way to determine if a timeout has occurred.

      Constructor and Description
      ElapsedTime()
      Constructor which set the start time as the current time
